{"tid":646404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴警告皇馬不要挖走迪基亞","createTime":"2018-04-29T04:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T07:27:21.000Z","uid":20816,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1861cf10ef7878f229c1500b8f3a44bf37a67f46","tid":646404,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"摩連奴警告皇家馬德里不要亂來，不要嘗試簽入迪基亞，呼籲他們去其他球會買人解決龍門問題。<br />\n<br />\n皇馬一直喜歡迪基亞，2015年差點買入此子，但最後未能成事。現時迪基亞的合約去到2019年，不過皇馬仍然虎視眈眈。<br />\n摩連奴警告說，迪基亞一定會留在曼聯比賽，呼籲皇馬死心不要搶人。<br />\n摩連奴說：「迪基亞會留隊，我不知道皇馬的意圖，但如果我是他們，我會另找他人。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=RmHe%2F8bsTW7GfwpB%2FNHOFl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9bfd7db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.goal.com/zh-hk/新聞/摩連奴-警告-皇馬-不要挖走-迪基亞/fwkmfd1802af140jouznlho9g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%91%A9%E9%80%A3%E5%A5%B4-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E7%9A%87%E9%A6%AC-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%8C%96%E8%B5%B0-%E8%BF%AA%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%9E%2Ffwkmfd1802af140jouznlho9g&d=RmHe%2F8bsTW7GfwpB%2FNHOFl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e579dd9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.goal.com/zh-hk/新聞/摩連奴-警告-皇馬-不要挖走-迪基亞/fwkmfd1802af140jouznlho9g</a>"},{"pid":"a91766ed89aba1e0587c80f35f49893f71db740c","tid":646404,"uid":84013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T04:54:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母雲高爾"},{"pid":"e136dc4368e6c66b72362cb307bca900b8bfaa6d","tid":646404,"uid":22138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"照買會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5960b2bce3fc15242a7b32315c948127d49b2c","tid":646404,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e136dc4368e6c66b72362cb307bca900b8bfaa6d","tid":6